			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>No, it's not 5 DPS.  It adds 5 to the bonus damage for offhand weapons.  Notice that for primary hand, you have a bonus damage of 13 at level 65.  That means 13 damage is added to every primary hand hit.  Normally, there is NO bonus to off hand damage.  With SS it now has 5 damage which means it would be a minimum of 5 damage per hit -- not specifically 5 DPS.</span></td>
